Posted By: Craig D
Hi,

I have available for sale a very nice T3 Turkey Red of Big Ed Walsh.  The card is graded PSA-5(MK). Happy to send front and back scans. Easily one of the prettiest T3s.  

I'd ask $1250 OBO, shipping and insurance included.

Thanks,
Craig
